possible, I would like the game to track stats, like questions answered correctly &amp; so on.<br /><br />I don't know if I want the questions to be timed or not yet.<br /><br />If anyone is interested in making this idea into a game, just let me know. Advice &amp; criticism is welcomed.<br /><br />Thanks!<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4551">Timmy112384</a> — Sun Aug 29, 2010 8:29 pm</p><hr />
